  "objective": "Add three new exchange integrations to CryptoExchanges.Net in strict priority order — (1) Bybit, (2) OKX, (3) Bitget — for a global (non-US) audience. Each exchange clones the verified Binance pattern (Core → Http → Exchange → DI, DeltaMapper DTO→model, bespoke ISymbolMapper, retry-only-on-GET, per-attempt re-signing). The signing/credential abstraction is generalized after Bybit, against OKX, and Bitget then reuses that abstraction.",
